 one. The board says that the $12.76 one is a mirage, that it won=E2=80=99t=
 actually close, but wouldn=E2=80=99t you be pretty tempted? Shareholders a=
re: The stock has traded above $11.15 for the last three weeks or so, and c=
losed yesterday at $12.02, suggesting that shareholders expect to do better=
