<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Alastair Borthwick, Bank of America=E2=80=99s =
chief financial officer, added to the criticism on Monday, saying the Fed=
=E2=80=99s proposals could mean risk-weighted assets are double counted in =
some instances, which could again constrain bank lending.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CI think there=E2=80=99s going to be s=
ome important points of advocacy on the part of industry and by businesses =
in America, who are the ones who ultimately are going to pay for this,=E2=
=80=9D Borthwick told the Barclays conference.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">And then there is Jamie Dimon complaining that=
 <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32686879.258425/a=
HR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDktMTEvZGltb24t=
c2xhbXMtcmVndWxhdG9ycy1vbi1jYXBpdGFsLXBsYW5zLXVyZ2VzLW1vcmUtaHVtaWxpdHk_Y21=
waWQ9QkJEMDkxMjIzX01PTkVZU1RVRkYmdXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbCZ1dG1fc291cmNlPW5ld3=
NsZXR0ZXImdXRtX3Rlcm09MjMwOTEyJnV0bV9jYW1wYWlnbj1tb25leXN0dWZm/607f07ceef4b=
8524a319a23cB6e13a155" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" targe=
t=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; bor=
der-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: s=
olid; background-color: #ccc;">  more capital is too much</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Jamie Dimon again took aim at higher capital r=
equirements US regulators proposed for the banking industry in July, saying=
 he would =E2=80=9Clove to know what they really want to accomplish.=E2=80=
=9D</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Requiring US lenders to hold more capital than=
 their international competitors is a =E2=80=9Chuge negative=E2=80=9D over =
time, the JPMorgan Chase &amp; Co. chief executive officer said Monday at a=
 conference hosted by Barclays Plc. Regulators should have shared more abou=
t the =E2=80=9Ccost-benefit to society,=E2=80=9D said Dimon, who questioned=
 whether they learned the right lessons from the failures earlier this year=
 of Silicon Valley Bank and First Republic Bank.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;"><a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness=
.com/click/32686879.258425/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZnQuY29tL2NvbnRlbnQvY2NkMGY2OGMt=
MjU0My00ZTAyLWJiYmMtMDEwMWQwNDYwOWUx/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cC6acdc0f5" ite=
mprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"colo=
r: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; bor=
der-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #c=
cc;">And</a>:=C2=A0</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CDo [regulators] want bank=
s ever to be investable again?=E2=80=9D Dimon said at an industry conferenc=
e organised by Barclays. =E2=80=9CI wouldn=E2=80=99t be a big buyer of bank=
s=E2=80=89.=E2=80=89.=E2=80=89.=E2=80=89I=E2=80=99d be no better than equal=
 weight, or whatever you call it,=E2=80=9D he told the audience of analysts=
 and investors.</p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I love that Jamie Dimon obviously=C2=A0<em>can=
=C2=A0</em>speak in the language of sell-side stock analysts, but he finds =
it somewhat distasteful. =E2=80=9CEqual weight, or whatever you call it.=E2=
=80=9D Also he is skeptical about those =E2=80=9Cimportant points of advoca=
cy=E2=80=9D:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The Fed is now soliciting comments on the prop=
osed changes in a notice of proposed rulemaking (NPR) but Dimon was sceptic=
al that any material changes would be made.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CDo you think the NPRs are going to ma=
ke a =E2=80=A6 difference?=E2=80=9D Dimon said, in his characteristically b=
lunt style.<a class=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#footnote-5" style=3D"color:=
 #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; borde=
r-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: none !important; background-c=
olor: transparent !important; display: inline-block;">
<span>[5]</span>
</a>=C2=A0=E2=80=9CIt=E2=80=99s my academics arguing with their academics. =
They=E2=80=99re going to do what they want anyway. That=E2=80=99s all that=
=E2=80=99s going to happen.=E2=80=9D</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The basic point here is that the nuances might=
 get fixed, but US banks will still have to have more capital, and Dimon do=
esn=E2=80=99t like that.</p>
