; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-sty=
le: solid; background-color: #ccc;">rough count</a> is that current insider=
s (Levin et al.) own about 27% of the votes and disgruntled ex-insiders (Oc=
h, Shafir) own perhaps half that, so it will be a bit harder for Sculptor t=
o win the second vote of disinterested outsiders.</p>
